Package: esquisse
Type: Package
Title: Explore and Visualize Your Data Interactively
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(person("Fanny", "Meyer", email = "fanny.meyer@dreamrs.fr", role = c("aut")),
  person("Victor", "Perrier", email = "victor.perrier@dreamrs.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: <victor.perrier@dreamrs.fr>
Description: A Shiny gadget to create ggplot charts interactively with drag-and-drop to map your variables.
    You can quickly visualize your data accordingly to their type, export to 'PNG' or 'PowerPoint', and retrieve the code to reproduce the chart.
